tomorrow, at 7am, jade and i will have been officially together for one month.. god.. this has been the greatest day i've ever lived.. truly the greatest month of my life... the most perfect month i could ever want.. and the greatest thing is, i know that things are, and will just keep getting better... most people treasure the first week, and then the first month, and then, eventually the first year.. but with jade and i.. with us.. it wont be part of treasuring the first month or year.. because every day, every minute, every moment will be treasured..
god.. i love her.. so much.. she's the ONE "
event,"people these days actually amaze me..

you see.. i have these friends.. and they're hurt because some of their friends (who also happen to be my friends) said some stuff.. and it hurt them.. it just made them feel bad because they're not used to hearing it or feeling what they made them feel.. so they come to me.. and they feel hurt.. and they talk about how much it sucks to feel this way.. and one even told me that i have no idea what it feels like to feel this way..

which leads to me to part that amazes me.. these people.. that are so hurt and feel so badly now.. make me feel this way all the time.. all the time.. what happened to them, they do to me constantly.. sometimes weekly.. it's not so much that it hurts anymore, not like it used to anyways.. when it first started happening to me, it felt almost unbearable because it happened almost daily.. but now.. after years.. i've actually become numb (for the most part) to the feeling.. it still hurts occasionally, especially when it pertains to something i enjoy or would have.. but they act like it's the worst feeling in the world..

now.. dont get me wrong.. at times, it really is the worst feeling in the world.. but they're the ones who usually give it to people.. they're the ones that usually make other people feel that way.. and now.. hehe.. i know it's wrong.. i know that i shouldnt laugh, but i cant really help myself.. it's amazing.. it really is.. to see them, and hear them complain so much.. they dont truly know what it's like to feel that way.. no one does until the experiance over and over and over again, especially from their closest friends...
[to these people, who will remain unnamed]] feel it over and over and over for about 8 years and then get back to me on how it feels..."
jade and i have officially been together since monday.. god she's amazing... it feels like years of being together...

and some of the best friends i've ever known.. and lost.. are back.. hehe.. that didnt make much sense, did it? hehe.. well.. anne is talking to me again.. and, while no one really knows what that means to me, maybe she does.. thanx for bein back anne!! and jen liu.. she's back too.. hehe.. yeah.. that was an interesting interlude.. but she's back.. and it's good.. thanx jen!!

but.. with all good must come some bad.. and it's beginning to feel like two more have gone.. i wont say who.. but it hurts.. especially when you walk by and they just brush you off like, ""oh.. hey..."" and they keep walking.. before this week.. it would've been like, ""HEY!!"" with a big hug and everything.. //sigh// my life sucks sometimes...
but i'm happy :-) hehe.. so most of my life doesnt suck... and truthfully.. when i'm with jade.. none of it does.. she makes all my troubles disappear...
well.. tomorrow is a game.. whoopdeedo.. hehe.. yeah.. that made total sense.. we'll see if i see anyone i know from warren (which is like two people)

event,"well.. i know i haven't written since like tuesday.. but there's not really much to make daily entries about.. so i think i'll do a recap.. so here's what's to come if you choose to keep reading..

lindsay is not the one for me.. it's that simple.. jade kinda helped me realize that.. but i dun think she knows it.. and the fact that she kinda totally ignored me online the other day.. well.. yeah.. she's not the one.. which leads me to..

i've moved on from lindsay.. 3 years without saying a word should've been enough.. but now.. it was jojo telling me that i wasnt the only one who could see me with this other gurl.. and the more and more i talk to this gurl.. she makes me think we'd make a better match more and more.. and i know connie is saying to herself right now 'dont get your hopes up jake..' well... no worries con bon.. i've begun to stop getting my hopes up.. i'm just.. i dunno.. well.. even if i am getting my hopes up.. they're not that high yet.. so dont worry.. okay?
well.. i'm drum major again.. cool to me.. i dunno about anyone else... haha.. so.. yeah.. congrats to ulysses, cary, and jen..
well.. that just about sums up my entire week.. kinda boring if you ask me.. but.. yeah.. haha.. anyways.. off to do more stuff.. dunno what exactly.. but stuff.. haha... laterdayz..."
event,"too tired to do a full update.. let's cut it down big time...
i spent the day taking pictures.. worrying about tryouts.. and thinking of her.. yeah.. i thought about her a lot.. something about her.. mann...
oh well.. ask me about it [and her] and i'll tell you some time... laterdayz..."

i am soooo totally scared tonite... i feel like barfing or something.. tryouts are tomorrow and i'm totally scared outta my pants that i wont make head drum major.. and i know i shouldnt be worried about that.. that i should be worried about stuff like.. just making and drum major spot period.. but there's so much stuff that i'm worried about now..  if i dun make it and ulysses does.. will everyone be like  ""maybe we should've chosen ulysses last year"" and stuff like that.. i mean.. just all the second guessing is scaring me so much.. and then stuff like... if i'm not parade DM.. that means that i have to march trumpet.. which i suck at.. seriously.. i may play good standing still.. but i suck moving.. damn... oh well.. wish me luck tomorrow.. please?? haha..

well.. other then that my day was okay i guess.. i gotta talk to narumi tomorrow about what they did to kyle today.. and uhmm.. what else.. i dunno.. i'm not thinking right now.. wayy too freaking scared... well.. ttyl...
event,"man.. it's late.. i should get some sleep.. but first.. my day..

hehe.. today was pretty boring in the morning.. woke up.. ate pb&j [i'd been craving it since last night.. hehe...] and then i sat around and watched some little league baseball.. curacao kicked some US BUTT.. hehe.. that was fun to watch.. no hitter if i remember right.. 6-zip.. so..yeah..

after that my parents picked me up to go eat and  then to buy my dad's new car.. he bought a beamer.. a 325 i.. hehe.. it's nice.. not as nice as the 350z i want.. but nice anyways.. so.. yeah.. and now the jimmy is all mine.. hehe.. anyways..

so then we came home and i watched teh championship game and japan kicked more US butt.. hehe.. oh yeah.. that was awesome.. 10-1.. and they only got the 1 on a fluke.. so.. yeah.. anyways.. uhmm.. after that i cleaned a bit and chatted a bit.. and then dinner.. and then more chatting and making this.. and now.. here i am.. typing away at 11.30.. hehe..

well.. second week of preseason tomorrow.. gotta love it.. especially since i have a dm clinic tomorrow.. hehe.. tryouts wednesday.. it'll be awesome.. oh yeah.. just about got my routine.. ask me to see it and i'll show you..
well.. imma go now.. laterdayz... sweet dreams.."
